  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ElasticSearchController
    Description:
    This controllers purpose is to interact directly with the Elastic Search server for the application and query it for information.
    ElasticSearchController.CheckConnectionTask
    Checks the connection to the Elastic Search database.
    ElasticSearchController.DeleteCareProviderTask
    Delete a Care Provider from the Elastic Search database
    ElasticSearchController.DeletePatientTask
    Delete a patient from the Elastic Search database.
    ElasticSearchController.DeletePhotoTask
    Delete a Photo from the Elastic Search database.
    ElasticSearchController.LoadCareProviderTask
    Load a Care Provider from the Elastic Search database.
    ElasticSearchController.LoadPatientTask
    Load a patient from the Elastic Search database.
    ElasticSearchController.LoadPhotoTask
    Load a Photo from the Elastic Search database.
    ElasticSearchController.SaveCareProviderTask
    Saves a Care Provider to the Elastic Search Database
    ElasticSearchController.SavePatientTask
    Saves a patient to the Elastic Search Database.
    ElasticSearchController.SavePhotoTask
    Saves a Photo to the Elastic Search Database.
    PatientController
    Description:
    The controller for all changes made to a Patient.
    ProblemController
    Description:
    The controller for all changes made to a Problem.
    ProviderController
    Description:
    The controller for all changes made to a Care Provider.
    SyncController

    The controller designed to sync changes between offline and online.
